snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 - The First Preview | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Check out our first Warhammer 40K: Space Marine 2 preview, which so far, has at the very least fully captured the grimdark spirit of the fearless Adeptus Astartes.

Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 is coming to PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC in 2023.

Stay tuned for more exciting IGN coverage at gamescom 2023!

#IGN #Gaming #Warhammer
